<H2><A NAME="SECTION0216150000000000000000">
3.6.15 Transformations</A>
</H2>

<P>
<i>GetTransform is a beta function</i>

<P>
<dl><dd><pre class="verbatim">
virtual const OETrans &amp;GetTransform() const = 0
</pre></dl>

<P>
Returns an OETrans, which is a container of all the transformations which
have been applied to the OEConfBaseT.  This function is particularly useful
when the internal representation of coordinates may not be Cartesian.

<P>
<dl><dd><pre class="verbatim">
virtual void Transform(const OETransBase *) = 0
virtual void Transform(const OETrans &amp;) = 0
</pre></dl>

<P>
Applies the geometric transformation specified in the OETransBase* object
or the series of geometric transformations specified in the OETran container
to the OEConfBaseT.  These functions permanently change the coordinates of
the OEConfBaseT.

<P>

